 rвҶҗTest_BuildPackage_072(stopFlag batchFlag);вҺ•TRAP;path;zipFileName;msg;rc;parms;tempPath;list;buff
вҚқ Build package and use the `exclude` property with two files and one dir but "wrong" casing
вҚқ Under Windows that must not matter, which is why it's not executed elsewhere
 вҺ•TRAPвҶҗ(999 'C' '. вҚқ Deliberate error')(0 'N')
 rвҶҗT._Failed

 :If 'Win'вүў3вҶ‘вҠғ# вҺ•WG'APLVersion'
     rвҶҗT._WindowsOnly вӢ„ вҶ’0
 :EndIf

 tempPathвҶҗвҲҶGetTempDir''
 pathвҶҗвҲҶTEMP_TEST_DATA,'/Build/NuGet2/'
 parmsвҶҗTC.CreateBuildParms path
 parms.licenseWarningвҶҗ0
 parms.targetPathвҶҗtempPath
 zipFileNameвҶҗTC.BuildPackage parms
 listвҶҗTC.ZipArchive.ListZipContents zipFileName
 buffвҶҗвҚ•вҚӘlist
 вҶ’T.PassesIf 0=вҲЁ/вҲЁ/'вҺ•IO.apla'вҚ·buff
 вҶ’T.PassesIf 0=вҲЁ/вҲЁ/'вҺ•ML.apla'вҚ·buff
 вҶ’T.PassesIf 0=вҲЁ/вҲЁ/'/Tests/'вҚ·buff

 rвҶҗT._OK

вҲҶTidyUp:
 F.DeleteFile zipFileName
 (rc msg)вҶҗF.RmDirByForce tempPath
 msg Assert rc=0
вҚқDone
